<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Custom Systems for Fabrication Shops</title>
    <style>
        /* --- Base & Reset --- */
        * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
        body { 
            font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; 
            line-height: 1.6; 
            color: #111827; 
            background-color: #e5e7eb; /* Industrial light grey background */
            padding: 20px; 
        }
        
        /* --- Main Container --- */
        .container { 
            max-width: 750px; /* Narrow width for easy reading */
            margin: 40px auto; 
            background: #ffffff; 
            padding: 50px 60px; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgba(0,0,0,0.1); 
        }
        
        /* --- Typography --- */
        h1 { 
            font-size: 2.8rem; 
            font-weight: 800; 
            line-height: 1.15; 
            margin-bottom: 20px; 
            letter-spacing: -0.03em; 
            color: #000000;
        }
        .subhead { 
            font-size: 1.3rem; 
            color: #4b5563; 
            margin-bottom: 30px; 
            font-weight: 500; 
        }
        h2 { 
            font-size: 1.75rem; 
            margin: 50px 0 20px; 
            border-bottom: 2px solid #f3f4f6; 
            padding-bottom: 10px; 
            color: #111827;
        }
        p { margin-bottom: 20px; font-size: 1.1rem; }
        
        /* --- Authority Block --- */
        .authority { 
            background: #fffbeb; 
            border-left: 5px solid #f59e0b; 
            padding: 20px 25px; 
            margin: 30px 0; 
            font-weight: 700; 
            color: #92400e; 
            font-size: 1.15rem; 
        }
        
        /* --- Highlights & Pricing --- */
        .highlight { color: #ea580c; font-weight: 700; }
        .price { font-size: 2.5rem; font-weight: 800; color: #000; margin: 10px 0; }
        .price-sub { font-size: 1.1rem; color: #4b5563; font-weight: 600; }
        
        /* --- Lists --- */
        ul { margin-bottom: 30px; list-style-type: none; }
        ul li { margin-bottom: 14px; padding-left: 35px; position: relative; font-size: 1.15rem; font-weight: 500;}
        ul.problem li::before { content: "⚠️"; position: absolute; left: 0; font-size: 1.2rem; }
        ul.solution li::before { content: "✅"; position: absolute; left: 0; font-size: 1.2rem; }
        ul.negative li { color: #6b7280; font-weight: 400; }
        ul.negative li::before { content: "❌"; position: absolute; left: 0; font-size: 1.2rem; }
        
        /* --- Form Section --- */
        .form-section { 
            background: #f9fafb; 
            padding: 40px; 
            border-radius: 8px; 
            margin-top: 50px; 
            border: 2px solid #e5e7eb; 
        }
        .form-section h3 { font-size: 1.5rem; margin-bottom: 10px; font-weight: 800;}
        .form-group { margin-bottom: 20px; }
        label { display: block; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 8px; font-size: 0.95rem; color: #374151; }
        input[type="text"], input[type="email"], input[type="file"] { 
            width: 100%; 
            padding: 14px 15px; 
            border: 1px solid #d1d5db; 
            border-radius: 6px; 
            font-size: 1rem; 
            background: #fff;
            transition: border-color 0.2s; 
        }
        input[type="text"]:focus, input[type="email"]:focus { 
            outline: none; 
            border-color: #ea580c; 
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 3px rgba(234, 88, 12, 0.1); 
        }
        
        /* --- Button --- */
        button { 
            display: block; 
            width: 100%; 
            background-color: #ea580c; /* High contrast industrial orange */
            color: #ffffff; 
            border: none; 
            padding: 20px; 
            font-size: 1.25rem; 
            font-weight: 800; 
            border-radius: 6px; 
            cursor: pointer; 
            transition: background-color 0.2s, transform 0.1s; 
            margin-top: 10px;
        }
        button:hover { background-color: #c2410c; }
        button:active { transform: scale(0.98); }
        
        /* --- Helper Text --- */
        .guarantee { text-align: center; font-size: 1rem; color: #111827; margin-top: 15px; font-weight: 700; }
        .note { font-size: 1rem; color: #4b5563; margin-bottom: 25px; }
        
        /* --- Mobile Responsiveness --- */
        @media (max-width: 600px) {
            .container { padding: 30px 20px; margin: 10px auto; }
            h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
            .form-section { padding: 25px 15px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="container">
    
    <h1>Stop Buying Software. Build a System That Actually Fits Your Shop.</h1>
    <p class="subhead">Most fabrication shops are losing time and money in broken spreadsheets and rushed quotes. We fix that with a system built specifically for how you work.</p>
    
    <div class="authority">
        Built from experience behind $16M+ in awarded fabrication work.
    </div>

    <h2>Does Any of This Sound Familiar?</h2>
    <ul class="problem">
        <li>Quotes are inconsistent</li>
        <li>Scope gets missed</li>
        <li>Labour is guessed</li>
        <li>The shop is fixing problems from estimating</li>
        <li>You’re always rushed and reacting</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="highlight">👉 Bottom line: Your system isn’t working.</p>

    <h2>The Solution</h2>
    <p>We build you a custom system in Excel that:</p>
    <ul class="solution">
        <li>Matches how you actually quote</li>
        <li>Connects material, labour, and scope</li>
        <li>Reduces mistakes and rework</li>
        <li>Gives you confidence in every number</li>
    </ul>
    
    <p><strong>What you won't get:</strong></p>
    <ul class="negative">
        <li>No generic software.</li>
        <li>No endless monthly subscriptions.</li>
        <li>No unnecessary complexity.</li>
    </ul>
    <p><em>Just something that works.</em></p>

    <h2>The Investment</h2>
    <div class="price">$7,500 one-time</div>
    <p class="price-sub">👉 That’s about $30/week over 5 years.</p>
    <p><em>(Less than 1 hour of shop labour.)</em></p>

    <div class="form-section">
        <h3>Let's see what's missing.</h3>
        <p class="note">Send me one of your recent quotes. I’ll show you what’s missing. Or, I’ll map out your system before you commit to anything.</p>
        
        <form action="https://formsubmit.co/gregwsheldon@gmail.com" method="POST" enctype="multipart/form-data">
            
            <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="New Quote Review Request!">

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="name">Name</label>
                <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required placeholder="John Doe">
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="company">Company</label>
                <input type="text" id="company" name="company" required placeholder="Your Fabrication Shop">
            </div>
            
            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="email">Email</label>
                <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="john@example.com">
            </div>

            <div class="form-group">
                <label for="file">Upload a recent quote (Optional)</label>
                <input type="file" id="file" name="attachment" accept=".pdf,.doc,.docx,.xls,.xlsx,.csv">
            </div>

            <button type="submit">Send me my quote review</button>
            <p class="guarantee">If I don’t find anything valuable, I’ll tell you.</p>
        </form>
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>
